## 🗺️ Visual Summary

```
What you write locally:          What AWS runs:
─────────────────────────        ─────────────────────────────────────
src/handlers/        ──CDK──►   Lambda Function
src/agent/           ──CDK──►   (same Python code, running in cloud)
src/mcp_servers/     ──CDK──►
infra/stacks/        ──CDK──►   VPC + Alarm + EventBridge Rule + IAM Role
.env                 ──you──►   Lambda Environment Variables (set manually)
```
